{
  "video_id": "WHjKnNbYiOs",
  "title": "How I'm discovering the secrets of ancient texts | Gregory Heyworth",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12760.0,
      "end_time": 15456.0,
      "text": "On January 26, 2013,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15480.0,
      "end_time": 18976.0,
      "text": "a band of al-Qaeda militants entered the ancient city of Timbuktu"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19000.0,
      "end_time": 21000.0,
      "text": "on the southern edge of the Sahara Desert."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21640.0,
      "end_time": 26256.0,
      "text": "There, they set fire to a medieval library of 30,000 manuscripts"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26280.0,
      "end_time": 29560.0,
      "text": "written in Arabic and several African languages"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29800.0,
      "end_time": 34815.0,
      "text": "and ranging in subject from astronomy to geography, history to medicine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 34840.0,
      "end_time": 36536.0,
      "text": "including one book which records"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 36560.0,
      "end_time": 40480.0,
      "text": "perhaps the first treatment for male erectile dysfunction."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 41760.0,
      "end_time": 43560.0,
      "text": "Unknown in the West,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 43800.0,
      "end_time": 46495.0,
      "text": "this was the collected wisdom of an entire continent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 46520.0,
      "end_time": 50600.0,
      "text": "the voice of Africa at a time when Africa was thought not to have a voice at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 51480.0,
      "end_time": 53976.0,
      "text": "The mayor of Bamako, who witnessed the event,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 54000.0,
      "end_time": 55936.0,
      "text": "called the burning of the manuscripts"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 55960.0,
      "end_time": 58200.0,
      "text": "\"a crime against world cultural heritage.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 58880.0,
      "end_time": 60416.0,
      "text": "And he was right --"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 60440.0,
      "end_time": 63879.0,
      "text": "or he would have been, if it weren&#39;t for the fact that he was also lying."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 64560.0,
      "end_time": 67296.0,
      "text": "In fact, just before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 67320.0,
      "end_time": 71455.0,
      "text": "African scholars had collected a random assortment of old books"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 71480.0,
      "end_time": 73976.0,
      "text": "and left them out for the terrorists to burn."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 74000.0,
      "end_time": 76936.0,
      "text": "Today, the collection lies hidden in Bamako,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 76959.0,
      "end_time": 78336.0,
      "text": "the capital of Mali,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 78360.0,
      "end_time": 80456.0,
      "text": "moldering in the high humidity."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 80480.0,
      "end_time": 82336.0,
      "text": "What was rescued by ruse"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 82360.0,
      "end_time": 84960.0,
      "text": "is now once again in jeopardy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 84120.0,
      "end_time": 85360.0,
      "text": "this time by climate."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 86200.0,
      "end_time": 88616.0,
      "text": "But Africa, and the far-flung corners of the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 88640.0,
      "end_time": 90936.0,
      "text": "are not the only places, or even the main places"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 90960.0,
      "end_time": 95256.0,
      "text": "in which manuscripts that could change the history of world culture"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 95280.0,
      "end_time": 96800.0,
      "text": "are in jeopardy."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 97920.0,
      "end_time": 102656.0,
      "text": "Several years ago, I conducted a survey of European research libraries"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 102680.0,
      "end_time": 104936.0,
      "text": "and discovered that, at the barest minimum,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 104960.0,
      "end_time": 108175.0,
      "text": "there are 60,000 manuscripts"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 108200.0,
      "end_time": 109816.0,
      "text": "pre-1500"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 109840.0,
      "end_time": 112776.0,
      "text": "that are illegible because of water damage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 112800.0,
      "end_time": 116776.0,
      "text": "fading, mold and chemical reagents."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 116800.0,
      "end_time": 119776.0,
      "text": "The real number is likely double that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 119800.0,
      "end_time": 121976.0,
      "text": "and that doesn&#39;t even count"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 122000.0,
      "end_time": 124616.0,
      "text": "Renaissance manuscripts and modern manuscripts"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 124640.0,
      "end_time": 127760.0,
      "text": "and cultural heritage objects such as maps."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 129960.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132416.0,
      "text": "What if there were a technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 132440.0,
      "end_time": 137776.0,
      "text": "that could recover these lost and unknown works?"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 137800.0,
      "end_time": 142216.0,
      "text": "Imagine worldwide how a trove of hundreds of thousands"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 142240.0,
      "end_time": 145176.0,
      "text": "of previously unknown texts"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 145200.0,
      "end_time": 148239.0,
      "text": "could radically transform our knowledge of the past."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 150280.0,
      "end_time": 154296.0,
      "text": "Imagine what unknown classics we would discover"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 154320.0,
      "end_time": 157656.0,
      "text": "which would rewrite the canons of literature, history,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 157680.0,
      "end_time": 159120.0,
      "text": "philosophy, music --"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 159840.0,
      "end_time": 163376.0,
      "text": "or, more provocatively, that could rewrite our cultural identities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 163400.0,
      "end_time": 166760.0,
      "text": "building new bridges between people and culture."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 167520.0,
      "end_time": 170560.0,
      "text": "These are the questions that transformed me"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 170800.0,
      "end_time": 172896.0,
      "text": "from a medieval scholar, a reader of texts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 172920.0,
      "end_time": 174720.0,
      "text": "into a textual scientist."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 176120.0,
      "end_time": 178416.0,
      "text": "What an unsatisfying word \"reader\" is."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 178440.0,
      "end_time": 181160.0,
      "text": "For me, it conjures up images of passivity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 181400.0,
      "end_time": 183456.0,
      "text": "of someone sitting idly in an armchair"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 183480.0,
      "end_time": 185775.0,
      "text": "waiting for knowledge to come to him"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 185800.0,
      "end_time": 187496.0,
      "text": "in a neat little parcel."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 187520.0,
      "end_time": 190536.0,
      "text": "How much better to be a participant in the past,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 190560.0,
      "end_time": 193736.0,
      "text": "an adventurer in an undiscovered country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 193760.0,
      "end_time": 196160.0,
      "text": "searching for the hidden text."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 197360.0,
      "end_time": 199800.0,
      "text": "As an academic, I was a mere reader."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 200560.0,
      "end_time": 202976.0,
      "text": "I read and taught the same classics"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 203000.0,
      "end_time": 206136.0,
      "text": "that people had been reading and teaching for hundreds of years --"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 206160.0,
      "end_time": 209176.0,
      "text": "Virgil, Ovid, Chaucer, Petrarch --"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 209200.0,
      "end_time": 211536.0,
      "text": "and with every scholarly article that I published"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 211560.0,
      "end_time": 214760.0,
      "text": "I added to human knowledge in ever-diminishing slivers of insight."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 216760.0,
      "end_time": 218335.0,
      "text": "What I wanted to be"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 218360.0,
      "end_time": 220456.0,
      "text": "was an archaeologist of the past,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 220480.0,
      "end_time": 222550.0,
      "text": "a discoverer of literature,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 222800.0,
      "end_time": 223976.0,
      "text": "an Indiana Jones without the whip --"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 224000.0,
      "end_time": 225496.0,
      "text": "or, actually, with the whip."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 225520.0,
      "end_time": 226736.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 226760.0,
      "end_time": 230456.0,
      "text": "And I wanted it not just for myself but I wanted it for my students as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 230480.0,
      "end_time": 234375.0,
      "text": "And so six years ago, I changed the direction of my career."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 234400.0,
      "end_time": 237416.0,
      "text": "At the time, I was working on \"The Chess of Love,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 237440.0,
      "end_time": 240296.0,
      "text": "the last important long poem of the European Middle Ages"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 240320.0,
      "end_time": 241936.0,
      "text": "never to have been edited."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 241960.0,
      "end_time": 244976.0,
      "text": "And it wasn&#39;t edited because it existed in only one manuscript"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 245000.0,
      "end_time": 248256.0,
      "text": "which was so badly damaged during the firebombing of Dresden"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 248280.0,
      "end_time": 249496.0,
      "text": "in World War II"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 249520.0,
      "end_time": 252400.0,
      "text": "that generations of scholars had pronounced it lost."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 253400.0,
      "end_time": 256856.0,
      "text": "For five years, I had been working with an ultraviolet lamp"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 256880.0,
      "end_time": 258776.0,
      "text": "trying to recover traces of the writing"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 258800.0,
      "end_time": 261216.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;d gone about as far as technology at the time"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 261240.0,
      "end_time": 262616.0,
      "text": "could actually take me."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 262640.0,
      "end_time": 264736.0,
      "text": "And so I did what many people do."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 264760.0,
      "end_time": 266776.0,
      "text": "I went online,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 266800.0,
      "end_time": 268536.0,
      "text": "and there I learned about"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 268560.0,
      "end_time": 273136.0,
      "text": "how multispectral imaging had been used to recover two lost treatises"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 273160.0,
      "end_time": 276560.0,
      "text": "of the famed Greek mathematician Archimedes"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 276800.0,
      "end_time": 277616.0,
      "text": "from a 13th-century palimpsest."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 277640.0,
      "end_time": 280919.0,
      "text": "A palimpsest is a manuscript which has been erased and overwritten."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 282200.0,
      "end_time": 283455.0,
      "text": "And so, out of the blue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 283480.0,
      "end_time": 286536.0,
      "text": "I decided to write to the lead imaging scientist"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 286560.0,
      "end_time": 288776.0,
      "text": "on the Archimedes palimpsest project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 288800.0,
      "end_time": 290296.0,
      "text": "Professor Roger Easton,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 290320.0,
      "end_time": 292135.0,
      "text": "with a plan and a plea."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 292160.0,
      "end_time": 294200.0,
      "text": "And to my surprise, he actually wrote back."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 296000.0,
      "end_time": 299656.0,
      "text": "With his help, I was able to win a grant from the US government"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 299680.0,
      "end_time": 303696.0,
      "text": "to build a transportable, multispectral imaging lab,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 303720.0,
      "end_time": 308536.0,
      "text": "And with this lab, I transformed what was a charred and faded mess"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 308560.0,
      "end_time": 310560.0,
      "text": "into a new medieval classic."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 311360.0,
      "end_time": 314136.0,
      "text": "So how does multispectral imaging actually work?"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 314160.0,
      "end_time": 316616.0,
      "text": "Well, the idea behind multispectral imaging"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 316640.0,
      "end_time": 320936.0,
      "text": "is something that anyone who is familiar with infrared night vision goggles"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 320960.0,
      "end_time": 322335.0,
      "text": "will immediately appreciate:"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 322360.0,
      "end_time": 324856.0,
      "text": "that what we can see in the visible spectrum of light"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 324880.0,
      "end_time": 327200.0,
      "text": "is only a tiny fraction of what&#39;s actually there."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 327720.0,
      "end_time": 329920.0,
      "text": "The same is true with invisible writing."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 331280.0,
      "end_time": 335455.0,
      "text": "Our system uses 12 wavelengths of light"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 335480.0,
      "end_time": 337976.0,
      "text": "between the ultraviolet and the infrared,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 338000.0,
      "end_time": 341560.0,
      "text": "and these are shown down onto the manuscript from above"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 341800.0,
      "end_time": 342695.0,
      "text": "from banks of LEDs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 342720.0,
      "end_time": 344576.0,
      "text": "and another multispectral light source"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 344600.0,
      "end_time": 347553.0,
      "text": "which comes up through the individual leaves of the manuscript."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 347577.0,
      "end_time": 352960.0,
      "text": "Up to 35 images per sequence per leaf are imaged this way"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 352120.0,
      "end_time": 354740.0,
      "text": "using a high-powered digital camera equipped with a lens"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 354764.0,
      "end_time": 356736.0,
      "text": "which is made out of quartz."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 356760.0,
      "end_time": 358856.0,
      "text": "There are about five of these in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 358880.0,
      "end_time": 360695.0,
      "text": "And once we capture these images,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 360720.0,
      "end_time": 362776.0,
      "text": "we feed them through statistical algorithms"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 362800.0,
      "end_time": 365296.0,
      "text": "to further enhance and clarify them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 365320.0,
      "end_time": 368695.0,
      "text": "using software which was originally designed for satellite images"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 368720.0,
      "end_time": 372960.0,
      "text": "and used by people like geospatial scientists"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 372120.0,
      "end_time": 373320.0,
      "text": "and the CIA."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 374400.0,
      "end_time": 376336.0,
      "text": "The results can be spectacular."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 376360.0,
      "end_time": 378536.0,
      "text": "You may already have heard of what&#39;s been done"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 378560.0,
      "end_time": 379936.0,
      "text": "for the Dead Sea Scrolls,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 379960.0,
      "end_time": 381520.0,
      "text": "which are slowly gelatinizing."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 382480.0,
      "end_time": 386136.0,
      "text": "Using infrared, we&#39;ve been able to read even the darkest corners"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 386160.0,
      "end_time": 387880.0,
      "text": "of the Dead Sea Scrolls."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 388880.0,
      "end_time": 390336.0,
      "text": "You may not be aware, however,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 390360.0,
      "end_time": 393960.0,
      "text": "of other Biblical texts that are in jeopardy."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 393120.0,
      "end_time": 396536.0,
      "text": "Here, for example, is a leaf from a manuscript"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 396560.0,
      "end_time": 398336.0,
      "text": "that we imaged,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 398360.0,
      "end_time": 402240.0,
      "text": "which is perhaps the most valuable Christian Bible in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 402880.0,
      "end_time": 408656.0,
      "text": "The Codex Vercellensis is the oldest translation of the Gospels into Latin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 408680.0,
      "end_time": 411280.0,
      "text": "and it dates from the first half of the fourth century."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 412560.0,
      "end_time": 414816.0,
      "text": "This is the closest we can come"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 414840.0,
      "end_time": 418775.0,
      "text": "to the Bible at the time of the foundation of Christendom"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 418800.0,
      "end_time": 420416.0,
      "text": "under Emperor Constantine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 420440.0,
      "end_time": 422976.0,
      "text": "and at the time also of the Council of Nicaea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 423000.0,
      "end_time": 426496.0,
      "text": "when the basic creed of Christianity was being agreed upon."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 426520.0,
      "end_time": 429775.0,
      "text": "This manuscript, unfortunately, has been very badly damaged,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 429800.0,
      "end_time": 432160.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s damaged because for centuries"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 432400.0,
      "end_time": 434496.0,
      "text": "it had been used and handled"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 434520.0,
      "end_time": 437216.0,
      "text": "in swearing in ceremonies in the church."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 437240.0,
      "end_time": 441896.0,
      "text": "In fact, that purple splotch that you see in the upper left hand corner"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 441920.0,
      "end_time": 446216.0,
      "text": "is Aspergillus, which is a fungus"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 446240.0,
      "end_time": 449776.0,
      "text": "which originates in the unwashed hands"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 449800.0,
      "end_time": 451800.0,
      "text": "of a person with tuberculosis."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 452640.0,
      "end_time": 455695.0,
      "text": "Our imaging has enabled me to make the first transcription"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 455720.0,
      "end_time": 458320.0,
      "text": "of this manuscript in 250 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 459800.0,
      "end_time": 463256.0,
      "text": "Having a lab that can travel to collections where it&#39;s needed, however,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 463280.0,
      "end_time": 464760.0,
      "text": "is only part of the solution."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 465480.0,
      "end_time": 468336.0,
      "text": "The technology is expensive and very rare,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 468360.0,
      "end_time": 471576.0,
      "text": "and the imaging and image processing skills are esoteric."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 471600.0,
      "end_time": 473296.0,
      "text": "That means that mounting recoveries"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 473320.0,
      "end_time": 478216.0,
      "text": "is beyond the reach of most researchers and all but the wealthiest institutions."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 478240.0,
      "end_time": 481160.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s why I founded the Lazarus Project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 481400.0,
      "end_time": 482696.0,
      "text": "a not-for-profit initiative"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 482720.0,
      "end_time": 486696.0,
      "text": "to bring multispectral imaging to individual researchers"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 486720.0,
      "end_time": 490560.0,
      "text": "and smaller institutions at little or no cost whatsoever."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 491560.0,
      "end_time": 493176.0,
      "text": "Over the past five years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 493200.0,
      "end_time": 497560.0,
      "text": "our team of imaging scientists, scholars and students"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 497800.0,
      "end_time": 499256.0,
      "text": "has travelled to seven different countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 499280.0,
      "end_time": 503135.0,
      "text": "and have recovered some of the world&#39;s most valuable damaged manuscripts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 503160.0,
      "end_time": 506160.0,
      "text": "included the Vercelli Book, which is the oldest book of English,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 506184.0,
      "end_time": 508800.0,
      "text": "the Black Book of Carmarthen, the oldest book of Welsh,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 508824.0,
      "end_time": 512296.0,
      "text": "and some of the most valuable earliest Gospels"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 512320.00000000006,
      "end_time": 515200.00000000006,
      "text": "located in what is now the former Soviet Georgia."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 516600.0,
      "end_time": 519560.0,
      "text": "So, spectral imaging can recover lost texts."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 520360.0,
      "end_time": 525456.0,
      "text": "More subtly, though, it can recover a second story behind every object,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 525480.0,
      "end_time": 530176.0,
      "text": "the story of how, when and by whom a text was created,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 530200.0,
      "end_time": 533600.0,
      "text": "and, sometimes, what the author was thinking at the time he wrote."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 534600.0,
      "end_time": 537696.0,
      "text": "Take, for example, a draft of the Declaration of Independence"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 537720.0,
      "end_time": 540136.0,
      "text": "written in Thomas Jefferson&#39;s own hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 540160.0,
      "end_time": 542589.0,
      "text": "which some colleagues of mine imaged a few years ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 542613.0,
      "end_time": 543933.0,
      "text": "at the Library of Congress."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 544360.0,
      "end_time": 547560.0,
      "text": "Curators had noticed that one word throughout"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 547800.0,
      "end_time": 549456.0,
      "text": "had been scratched out and overwritten."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 549480.0,
      "end_time": 551560.0,
      "text": "The word overwritten was \"citizens.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 552240.0,
      "end_time": 554840.0,
      "text": "Perhaps you can guess what the word underneath was."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 555960.0,
      "end_time": 557376.0,
      "text": "\"Subjects.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 557400.0,
      "end_time": 560216.0,
      "text": "There, ladies and gentlemen, is American democracy"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 560240.0,
      "end_time": 562320.0,
      "text": "evolving under the hand of Thomas Jefferson."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 563360.0,
      "end_time": 567216.0,
      "text": "Or consider the 1491 Martellus Map,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 567240.0,
      "end_time": 569576.0,
      "text": "which we imaged at Yale&#39;s Beinecke Library."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 569600.0,
      "end_time": 572560.0,
      "text": "This was the map that Columbus likely consulted"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 572800.0,
      "end_time": 573776.0,
      "text": "before he traveled to the New World"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 573800.0,
      "end_time": 576536.0,
      "text": "and which gave him his idea of what Asia looked like"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 576560.0,
      "end_time": 578160.0,
      "text": "and where Japan was located."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 579640.0,
      "end_time": 582656.0,
      "text": "The problem with this map is that its inks and pigments"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 582680.0,
      "end_time": 584776.0,
      "text": "had so degraded over time"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 584800.0,
      "end_time": 586935.0,
      "text": "that this large, nearly seven-foot map,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 586960.0,
      "end_time": 589400.0,
      "text": "made the world look like a giant desert."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 589520.0,
      "end_time": 593136.0,
      "text": "Until now, we had very little idea, detailed idea, that is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 593160.0,
      "end_time": 594815.0,
      "text": "of what Columbus knew of the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 594840.0,
      "end_time": 596760.0,
      "text": "and how world cultures were represented."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 597240.0,
      "end_time": 601376.0,
      "text": "The main legend of the map was entirely illegible under normal light."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 601400.0,
      "end_time": 603656.0,
      "text": "Ultraviolet did very little for it."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 603680.0,
      "end_time": 605680.0,
      "text": "Multispectral gave us everything."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 606640.0,
      "end_time": 610216.0,
      "text": "In Asia, we learned of monsters with ears so long"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 610240.0,
      "end_time": 612560.0,
      "text": "that they could cover the creature&#39;s entire body."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 613400.0,
      "end_time": 617439.0,
      "text": "In Africa, about a snake who could cause the ground to smoke."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 618680.0,
      "end_time": 620935.0,
      "text": "Like starlight, which can convey images"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 620960.0,
      "end_time": 623536.0,
      "text": "of the way the Universe looked in the distant past,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 623560.0,
      "end_time": 627455.0,
      "text": "so multispectral light can take us back to the first stuttering moments"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 627480.0,
      "end_time": 628760.0,
      "text": "of an object&#39;s creation."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 629480.0,
      "end_time": 633416.0,
      "text": "Through this lens, we witness the mistakes, the changes of mind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 633440.0,
      "end_time": 636336.0,
      "text": "the naïvetés, the uncensored thoughts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 636360.0,
      "end_time": 638576.0,
      "text": "the imperfections of the human imagination"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 638600.0,
      "end_time": 641416.0,
      "text": "that allow these hallowed objects and their authors"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 641440.0,
      "end_time": 643960.0,
      "text": "to become more real,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 643120.0,
      "end_time": 645640.0,
      "text": "that make history closer to us."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 646760.0,
      "end_time": 648400.0,
      "text": "What about the future?"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 648480.0,
      "end_time": 650656.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s so much of the past,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 650680.0,
      "end_time": 653896.0,
      "text": "and so few people with the skills to rescue it"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 653920.0,
      "end_time": 657800.0,
      "text": "before these objects disappear forever."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 658480.0,
      "end_time": 661776.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s why I have begun to teach this new hybrid discipline"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 661800.0,
      "end_time": 663695.0,
      "text": "that I call \"textual science.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 663720.0,
      "end_time": 665336.0,
      "text": "Textual science is a marriage"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 665360.0,
      "end_time": 667736.0,
      "text": "of the traditional skills of a literary scholar --"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 667760.0,
      "end_time": 670295.0,
      "text": "the ability to read old languages and old handwriting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 670320.0,
      "end_time": 672160.0,
      "text": "the knowledge of how texts are made"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 672400.0,
      "end_time": 674175.0,
      "text": "in order to be able to place and date them --"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 674200.0,
      "end_time": 676936.0,
      "text": "with new techniques like imaging science,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 676960.0,
      "end_time": 679536.0,
      "text": "the chemistry of inks and pigments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 679560.0,
      "end_time": 681959.0,
      "text": "computer-aided optical character recognition."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 683160.0,
      "end_time": 685336.0,
      "text": "Last year, a student in my class,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 685360.0,
      "end_time": 686576.0,
      "text": "a freshman,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 686600.0,
      "end_time": 688416.0,
      "text": "with a background in Latin and Greek,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 688440.0,
      "end_time": 690776.0,
      "text": "was image-processing a palimpsest"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 690800.0,
      "end_time": 693520.0,
      "text": "that we had photographed at a famous library in Rome."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 694240.0,
      "end_time": 699000.0,
      "text": "As he worked, tiny Greek writing began to appear from behind the text."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 700200.0,
      "end_time": 701696.0,
      "text": "Everyone gathered around,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 701720.0,
      "end_time": 704376.0,
      "text": "and he read a line from a lost work"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 704400.0,
      "end_time": 706720.0,
      "text": "of the Greek comic dramatist Menander."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 707760.0,
      "end_time": 710456.0,
      "text": "This was the first time in well over a thousand years"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 710480.0,
      "end_time": 713400.0,
      "text": "that those words had been pronounced aloud."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 713880.0,
      "end_time": 716439.0,
      "text": "In that moment, he became a scholar."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 717440.0,
      "end_time": 720320.0,
      "text": "Ladies and gentlemen, that is the future of the past."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 720840.0,
      "end_time": 722560.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 722800.0,
      "end_time": 725800.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}